{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be lively and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Podcast Network</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #2c3e50;\n            color: #ecf0f1;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.8), rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.8)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/2c3e50/ffffff?text=Podcast+Network+Hero');\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .podcast-card {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .podcast-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n        .podcast-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #3498db;\n        }\n        .podcast-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n        }\n        .podcast-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .podcast-content p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: #555;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #3498db;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #2980b9;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #2c3e50;\n            color: #bdc3c7;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #3498db;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Tune In to Your Next Favorite Podcast</h1>\n        <p>Discover a universe of stories, insights, and entertainment from our diverse network of creators.</p>\n        <a href=\"#podcasts\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Podcasts</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"podcasts\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Featured Podcasts</h2>\n            <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/3498db/ffffff?text=Podcast+1\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 1\">\n                    <div class=\"podcast-content\">\n                        <h3>The Daily Grind</h3>\n                        <p>Insights and motivation for your everyday hustle. Hear from experts and everyday heroes.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2ecc71/ffffff?text=Podcast+2\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 2\">\n                    <div class=\"podcast-content\">\n                        <h3>Cosmic Conversations</h3>\n                        <p>Exploring the mysteries of the universe, from black holes to alien life.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e67e22/ffffff?text=Podcast+3\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 3\">\n                    <div class=\"podcast-content\">\n                        <h3>Storytime Central</h3>\n                        <p>Immerse yourself in captivating fictional tales across various genres.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/9b59b6/ffffff?text=Podcast+4\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 4\">\n                    <div class=\"podcast-content\">\n                        <h3>Tech Unpacked</h3>\n                        <p>Get the latest news and deep dives into the world of technology.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Become a Creator</h2>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 30px auto; line-height: 1.6;\">\n                Have a story to tell or knowledge to share? Join our growing network and reach a global audience. We provide the tools and support you need to succeed.\n            </p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Podcast Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Contact us: <a href=\"mailto:info@podcastnetwork.com\">info@podcastnetwork.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll animation for navigation links\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}